description: Here to bring you better food, it's Vore Food Truck! This is gourmet grilled cheese at it's very finest. With their vegan, vegetarian, and gluten-free options, this is a food truck for one and all! The Fearless, The Peruvian, and The Elvis are just the start with this amazing menu - grab a sandwich and get your choice of side and a cup of delicious tomato soup for a meal that will really fill you up! Don't miss out, visit Vore Food Truck today!
name: Vore Food Truck
